Package com.example.quacks_app

Class UserProfile

java.lang.Object
com.example.quacks_app.UserProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class UserProfile extends Object implements Serializable
The UserProfile class represents a user's profile information, including personal details, a profile picture, and an associated event list. It provides methods for accessing and modifying profile details and managing events.
